{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"close"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CancellableRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) "},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"title":"close(cancellable:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO20OutputStreamProtocolPAAE5close11cancellableSbAA14CancellableRefVSg_tKF","extendedModule":"GIO","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamProtocol\/close(cancellable:)-vjm3"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Closes the stream, releasing resources related to it."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/outputstreamprotocol\/close(cancellable:)-vjm3"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamProtocol"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"close","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CancellableRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV"},{"text":"? = nil) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Once the stream is closed, all other operations will return "},{"code":"closed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Closing a stream multiple times will not return an error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Closing a stream will automatically flush any outstanding buffers in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"stream."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Streams will be automatically closed when the last reference","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"is dropped, but you might want to call this function to make sure","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"resources are released as early as possible."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Some streams might keep the backing store of the stream (e.g. a file descriptor)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"open after the stream is closed. See the documentation for the individual","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"stream for details."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On failure the first error that happened will be reported, but the close"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"operation will finish as much as possible. A stream that failed to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"close will still return ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"closed"},{"type":"text","text":" for all operations. Still, it"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"is important to check and report the error to the user, otherwise"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"there might be a loss of data as all data might not be written."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"cancellable","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", then the operation can be cancelled by","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"code":"cancelled","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be returned.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Cancelling a close will still leave the stream closed, but there some streams","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"can use a faster close that doesn’t block to e.g. check errors. On"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"cancellation (as with any error) there is no guarantee that all written"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"data will reach the target."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/OutputStreamProtocol/close(cancellable:)-vjm3":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamProtocol\/close(cancellable:)-vjm3","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Closes the stream, releasing resources related to it."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"close","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CancellableRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"close(cancellable:)","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/outputstreamprotocol\/close(cancellable:)-vjm3","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/OutputStreamProtocol":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/OutputStreamProtocol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/outputstreamprotocol","abstract":[{"code":"GOutputStream","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is a base class for implementing streaming output."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OutputStreamProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OutputStreamProtocol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OutputStreamProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/CancellableRef":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/cancellableref","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GCancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" allows operations to be cancelled."}],"title":"CancellableRef"}}}